<h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>

<p>The Video Game Collective is designed around a loose group of projects in game development that have been proposed by members. Some are personal projects or extensions of existing projects from academic coursework. Anyone looking to help or just learn more about game design and creation are welcome.</p>

<h3 id="interests">Interests</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Java, C++, and C, and using OpenGL with these</li>
  <li>Python, using Pygame</li>
  <li>Blender</li>
  <li>Game Design</li>
</ul>

